StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETASSOCIATELECTURER
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETASSOCIATELECTURER(cAssociateLecturer OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cAssociateLecturer FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT AssociateLecturer_table.idPerson, AssociateLecturer_table.surname, AssociateLecturer_table.firstName, &lt;br/&gt; AssociateLecturer_table.title, AssociateLecturer_table.address, AssociateLecturer_table.phone, AssociateLecturer_table.postcode,&lt;br/&gt; AssociateLecturer_table.campusLocation, AssociateLecturer_table.idBuilding, AssociateLecturer_table.numberOffice,&lt;br/&gt; AssociateLecturer_table.staffType, &lt;br/&gt; AssociateLecturer_table.area, AssociateLecturer_table.lectureType,AssociateLecturer_table.numberHonours, AssociateLecturer_table.yearJoin&lt;br/&gt; FROM AssociateLecturer_table;&lt;br/&gt;END getAssociateLecturer;
